<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CSIRO Research Candidate Portal</title>


    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h2 class="text-center">Welcome to CSIRO Research Candidate Portal</h2>

        <p class="mt-4">
            This application allows candidates to apply for research positions in fields like Machine Learning and Data Science.
            Administrators can manage and sort applications based on GPA to select the top candidates for interviews.
        </p>

        <h3>For Candidates:</h3>
        <p>If you are a candidate, please register here:</p>
        <a href="/User/Register" class="btn btn-primary">Register as a Candidate</a><br />
        <a href="/Account/Login?role=user" class="btn btn-secondary mt-3">Candidate Login</a>

        <h3 class="mt-4">For Administrators:</h3>
        <p>If you are an administrator, you can log in here:</p>
        <a href="/Account/Login?role=admin" class="btn btn-secondary">Admin Login</a>

        <h3 class="mt-4">Application Instructions:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Register your contact details, GPA, course, and university.</li>
            <li>Ensure your GPA is 3.0 or higher and you’ve graduated from a top 100 university globally.</li>
            <li>Submit your application for review by the administrators.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS and dependencies (via CDN) -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>